    "description": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: #191813; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Prerequisite: Pact of the Tome feature</em></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: #191813; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">The complex sigils and symbols of ritual magic appear in your Book of Shadows. Choose two 1st-level spells that have the ritual tag. The spells appear in the book and don&rsquo;t count against the number of spells you know. While the book is in your possession, you can cast these spells as rituals. You can&rsquo;t cast the spells except as rituals, unless you&rsquo;ve learned them by some other means. You&nbsp;</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">can also cast a warlock spell you know as a ritual if it has the ritual tag.</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: #191813; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">When you find a spell with the ritual tag, you can transcribe it into your Book of Shadows if the spell&rsquo;s level is equal to or less than half your warlock level (rounded up). For each level of the spell, the transcription process takes 2 hours and costs 50 gold for the rare inks needed to inscribe it.</span></p>",
